<p>advantages freebies :&nbsp;</p>
<ol>
<li>industry boosted : TN gave women sewing machines and cycles =&gt; empowerment + employment&nbsp;</li>
<li>need based freebies : health and educatoin =&gt; productive workforce e.g. pandemic&nbsp;</li></ol>
<p>disadvantages freebies:</p>
<ol>
<li>macroeconomic stability + fiscal deficit : PN = 53% fiscal deficit</li>
<li>intergenerational inequality : RJ reverting old pension =&gt; 6% employee benefiting from 56% expenditure</li>
<li>Envt : power freebie =&gt; not green</li>
<li>agricultural :&nbsp; groundwater usage&nbsp;</li>
<li><strong>against free and fair elections </strong>
<ol>
<li>electoral malpractice : SC intervention</li></ol></li>
<li>moral hazard : impacts credit culture : loan waivers as freebies&nbsp;</li></ol>
<p><span style="color:#2ecc71">SL economic collapse raised question of state's role in free good and services.</span></p>
<p>Adopt route of achieving&nbsp;higher rates of economic growth. =&gt; race to efficiency&nbsp;</p>